{"version":"2026-04-12T08.42.36","description":"掘地三尺（DigDeep）- 敏感信息泄露检测工具，一键挖掘源码中的密码/密钥/手机号/身份证/云AK等敏感数据","homepage":"https://github.com/shine798/DigDeep","license":"unknown","url":"https://github.com/shine798/DigDeep/archive/refs/heads/main.zip#/DigDeep.zip","hash":"sha256:A853CA3ACAA6E1AA1A6264FA3BD0075817AD8F884E4B5F32EB1249466FD6C84C","extract_dir":"DigDeep-main","suggest":{"java":"main/oraclejdk8"},"pre_install":["Set-Content \"$dir\\DigDeep.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0', '@call oraclejdk8', '@start cmd /c java.exe -jar \"DigDeep.jar\" %*', '@popd' -Encoding Ascii"],"bin":"DigDeep.bat","checkver":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/shine798/DigDeep/commits","regex":"[\\d-]+T(\\d+):(\\d+):(\\d+)","replace":"$1$2.$3"},"autoupdate":{"url":"https://github.com/shine798/DigDeep/archive/refs/heads/main.zip#/DigDeep.zip"},"notes":["【工具类型】: 安全测试工具 | 信息泄露检测","【主要功能】: 挖掘源码中的密码、密钥、手机号、身份证、云AK等敏感信息","【适用场景】: 渗透测试、代码审计、源码泄漏排查","【技术特点】: 基于 Java 8，支持近百类敏感信息规则检测","【注意事项】: 需要 Java 环境，运行命令: java -jar DigDeep.jar"],"from":"https://github.com/bright-angel/scoop-bucket"}
